ithout resorting to disrespect or hate speech. Let's focus on the topic and learn from each other."', '"Great to see the positive and respectful conversation continuing here. Thank you, @parallel-parmesan, for your contribution."', '"@global-sharp, oh please, like your opinion is the only one that matters here. Can't we have some real debate instead of this PC nonsense?

